data.content:
noun
plural ~ vitae
[count] chiefly Brit :a short document that describes your education, work experience, etc. :rsum - called also CV, (US) vita
In U.S. English, a person who is applying for a job as a scientist, doctor, or professor at a college or university is asked to submit a curriculum vitae. For other jobs, the usual word in U.S. English is rsum.

(viết tắt CV) (từ Mỹ résumé)
bản lý lịch
